{"tid":558917,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職責？　自身職業觀點　蓋過　所有其他觀點　就是腐化了","createTime":"2018-02-12T16:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T16:46:52.000Z","uid":47714,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"02372cbc058d0b9d1be2621d112c0328b5685b22","tid":558917,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T16:46:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740.66479.273813022746352/1496910690436573/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100most%2Fphotos%2Fa.292832474177740.66479.273813022746352%2F1496910690436573%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2Bw0sMqiD850H8VGEI7V39hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=8020f951\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/100most/photos/a.292832474177740.66479.273813022746352/1496910690436573/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/dMViSG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FdMViSG&h=13bef1dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/港聞/159109/-人肉路障-兩死車禍前因-巡警示意慢駛-警-絕對合乎規則-\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2F159109%2F-%E4%BA%BA%E8%82%89%E8%B7%AF%E9%9A%9C-%E5%85%A9%E6%AD%BB%E8%BB%8A%E7%A6%8D%E5%89%8D%E5%9B%A0-%E5%B7%A1%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA%E6%84%8F%E6%85%A2%E9%A7%9B-%E8%AD%A6-%E7%B5%95%E5%B0%8D%E5%90%88%E4%B9%8E%E8%A6%8F%E5%89%87-&d=%2Bw0sMqiD850H8VGEI7V39hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=06baadba\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/港聞/159109/-人肉路障-兩死車禍前因-巡警示意慢駛-警-絕對合乎規則-</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10153601055207357\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcheng.lap.9%2Fposts%2F10153601055207357&d=%2Bw0sMqiD850H8VGEI7V39hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=b0f3ff3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cheng.lap.9/posts/10153601055207357</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：chenglap<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>所謂被權力腐化.</strong></span><br />\n對於當事人來說, 不過就是方便自己工作.<br />\n因為自己在努力工作, 方便工作的, 總是好事.<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當自身的職業觀點蓋過了所有其他觀點時, 就是腐化了.</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/leglory1988/photos/a.750270705067191.1073741828.603720966388833/933385196755740/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fleglory1988%2Fphotos%2Fa.750270705067191.1073741828.603720966388833%2F933385196755740%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=%2Bw0sMqiD850H8VGEI7V39hxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=823f1e27\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/leglory1988/photos/a.750270705067191.1073741828.603720966388833/933385196755740/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：光輝歲月<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-709Dd80_e5U/ViKj-Z9yY3I/AAAAAAAABFA/cZdQ2xdbcPI/s2048-Ic42/dark_police_force.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-709Dd80_e5U%2FViKj-Z9yY3I%2FAAAAAAAABFA%2FcZdQ2xdbcPI%2Fs2048-Ic42%2Fdark_police_force.jpg&h=8a72dc3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[課本不提的人物] 盧麒<br />\n<br />\n1. 盧麒 1966 年的時候, 十七歲, 職業是文員<br />\n2. 在反天星小輪加價時受到絕食行為的感召, 加入了絕食<br />\n3. 不久之後他遊行反對天星小輪加價<br />\n4. 盧麒向港府請願, 要求對方釋放示威者, 否則向英國法庭控告<br />\n5. 盧麒要求工聯會發動罷工罷課<br />\n6. 工聯會拒絕<br />\n7. 後來盧麒被警察扣留<br />\n8. 盧麒聲稱被警察毆打, 要他承認收了別人錢去搞事<br />\n9. 他被判簽保守行為三年後<br />\n10.之後被釋放<br />\n11.據說警方臥底在元朗, 向他指著一部單車, 聲稱這部單車是可以任盧麒使用<br />\n12.臥底說忘記帶匙, 叫他自己破鏈, 在他想要破鏈時, 警察衝出來將他拘捕<br />\n13.罪名是「偷單車」, 被判入獄四個月<br />\n14.盧麒聲稱在旺角警署拘留中被數十名警察輪流毒打<br />\n15.當中有些警察後來因為貪污而被捕<br />\n16.盧麒後來在居所中被發現跪著吊死<br />\n17.他的親人怕事, 不願意追究, 不了了之, 追悼者被判了入精神病院<br />\n18.香港暴動<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前睇過一則外國新聞　話有個警察遇到市民緊急情況　個情況我地認知係同個警察工作有衝突　佢好自然就幫左市民　記者問佢警察身份問題　佢話佢首先係人<br />\n我唔知有冇記錯新聞內容　不過好記得佢話首先是人<br />\n唔記得當時我睇呢則新聞係o係香港傳媒定台灣傳媒　記得件事係歐洲某個國家<br />\n有冇巴絲記得邊則新聞？"}]}